{"tid":1097604,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"買樓唔係好既投資工具","createTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T05:42:39.000Z","uid":27415,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f0f44d4cda1bd523b1d304c8a10fb1c4f201f2","tid":1097604,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"宜家樓價都升到咁盡，何必死追入去。<br />\n<br />\n不過買下其他金融產品，儲下錢先。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">斷估樓價唔會永遠都只升不跌掛？</span><br />\n<br />\n正常係應該有調整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然最大可能既短期調整就係減息，即係繼續推高個bubble，Bump大個樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係安慰自己咁睇，宜家入市係投資角度，<br />\n唔算好吸引姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2344fc2fdfcbff29615dd2278a943d86ad4d8fad","tid":1097604,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9c84a5b7866bc3fbdc03a34db7e8cc0aaa5f70","tid":1097604,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"好撚貴啊 DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9cf17ff2f97459c4a1de0da08b4cd44ab11a7f","tid":1097604,"uid":27415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"投資永遠係講：低買高賣<br />\n<br />\n既然年輕人都錯失曬D大升市，不如唔好諗買住<br />\n<br />\n儲下先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過千奇咪撚租啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n租又係好撚on9，兼推高個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1f6b1eb76999b3c2ada41deacd3085c6e49abb","tid":1097604,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"出去問十個香港人十個都係想買樓<br />\n剛需大到不得了<br />\n個個有錢就會想入市"},{"pid":"5fcc1758259a2c7b4105d9c664a6c39cd272a284","tid":1097604,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫只升不跌？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩叫通漲？"},{"pid":"423b42b0246881fd6c21aec394438dd0105b5771","tid":1097604,"uid":27415,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de1f6b1eb76999b3c2ada41deacd3085c6e49abb","tid":1097604,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"出去問十個香港人十個都係想買樓<br />\n剛需大到不得了<br />\n個個有錢就會想入市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"人人都好想買樓呢個係want姐<br />\n<br />\n好似港女全部好鍾意名牌手袋，連登仔全部好想投胎做富二代<br />\n<br />\n咁解釋唔到買樓係今時今日係咪一項好既investment呢？<br />\n<br />\n你宜家去買樓，分分鐘同港女20萬買愛馬仕差唔多架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況咁大筆錢要全部押注落去D磚頭，<br />\n如果你keep住cash係手咁去分注玩，你個個彈性大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你上車，係變供樓奴先，唔係即刻變業主。<br />\n<br />\n變相你會由高薪變失去財務自由，因為買樓即刻就背負好大既債務架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9301208c5e5e953695a7d22e5cf5327f8eddbe","tid":1097604,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcc1758259a2c7b4105d9c664a6c39cd272a284","tid":1097604,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫只升不跌？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩叫通漲？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"真係唔知....<br />\n好似係當所有物價一直升唔跌嗰陣就叫通漲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afa3d1234ff70d9b130ebcb00e2dc0e557d9b13","tid":1097604,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d9301208c5e5e953695a7d22e5cf5327f8eddbe","tid":1097604,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcc1758259a2c7b4105d9c664a6c39cd272a284","tid":1097604,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫只升不跌？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩叫通漲？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"真係唔知....<br />\n好似係當所有物價一直升唔跌嗰陣就叫通漲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"有通漲有通縮<br />\n你咪睇下通漲多定通縮多囉<br />\n你咪等下太古城幾時縮到返去十幾萬一層囉"},{"pid":"3635ce111122e34ec4340b3bb3e5862fc40f0973","tid":1097604,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"斷估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7904acbef97c004db